ms group of the univeral\nTeichm\\\"uller curve is the extended mapping class group. (3) The idea of a fine\nmoduli space. (4) The idea of using the period map to define a complex\nstructure on Teichm\\\"uller space.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Sep 2012 06:30:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-09-20"}
