egral system of general relativistic\nequations is to be solved and the outputs regularised for suppressing\ndivergences. Finally, for the provision of the computational power,\nparallelisation is under examination.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Sep 2012 12:49:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-09-11"}
