ive pulsar is distributed in frequencies lying nearby the\npulsar period. Even if the appearance of a sideband is already a signature of a\npulsar component, it may introduce an ambiguity in the determination of its\nperiod. We present here a method to solve the sideband issue.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Sep 2012 15:35:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-11"}
